Sometimes, a child character gives off the greatest, deepest revelations ever as cheesy as they are. 

How lucky am I to have something that makes saying goodbye so hard. ~ Winnie The Pooh

It doesn't hurt to keep looking for sunshine. ~Eeyore.

Remember this always: You're braver than you believe, and stronger than you seem, and smarter than you think. ~Winnie The Pooh

Sometimes people care too much, I think it's called love. ~Winnie The Pooh

